This paper deals with the segmentation of skin lesions in dermoscopic images, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The algorithm proposed in the paper involves the selection of the segmentation band, which is a technique used in information retrieval (cs.IR) to improve the accuracy of search results. The paper also presents experimental results achieved by the algorithm, which is a common practice in multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. Finally, the algorithm is automatic, which suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques.
